---
title: Cheesy Chicken Parmigiana with Bacon-Loaded Wedges & Apple Salad
description: A chicken parmigiana is a fan favourite that everyone will be excited about. How about adding a little twist to really get those cheers
of excitement going, like adding a side of bacon wedges? Three cheers for the chicken parmigiana!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/650b90eee5dab58ab5faeee4-a743a0c3.jpeg
